      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEY BUBBA LOUIE (1) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at 11 of 26 starts including seven wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (19.81) over 340m at Bulli. Form at the trip excellent including three wins. Drawn the fence and expected to go close. SLICK TEASE (2) was out of the placings last time when seventh at this track (19.31) but scored five back at this track (18.29). Solid record here at the distance winning three races. The form from his last run stacks up well. Cannot be left out. RED ROCK ALONG (8) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind True Request (18.59) in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Can measure up. GLOW STICK (7) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
